data.description: Looking for additional income to help with your mortgage payment.  No reason to look any further. This 3 bedroom 2 bath, can be split into a mother-in-law feature, or an additional income unit.  Wait... also, comes with an additional 2 bedroom 1 bath separate unit. Each having its own separate power meters, gas meters, and air conditioning. Definitely a must see.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from County Records.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
